  "detailed_description": "<strong>Join our discord:</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>While descending you will face various challenges that you will overcome by rolling, jumping and avoiding taking fall damage.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/d19d55e8a5dec697111828dbdfe19bc1.poster.avif?t=1645525200\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/d19d55e8a5dec697111828dbdfe19bc1.webm?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/d19d55e8a5dec697111828dbdfe19bc1.mp4?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Note: You can expect 1-2 hours of gameplay.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>You are a peasant that decides to take up the challenge of pursuing the tyrant king's lost crown. Your competitiveness and determination will shape you and your family's future, and the future of Eggland.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/f25d488f74b0c032e29a84e7a52c166b.poster.avif?t=1645525200\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/f25d488f74b0c032e29a84e7a52c166b.webm?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/f25d488f74b0c032e29a84e7a52c166b.mp4?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Downhill</h2>Your journey begins at the castle and will continue through different lower landscapes.<br>While descending you may take fall damage that can crack or even break your egg.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/8eda22dee4d3a8253ddf6a85add0778e.poster.avif?t=1645525200\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/8eda22dee4d3a8253ddf6a85add0778e.webm?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/8eda22dee4d3a8253ddf6a85add0778e.mp4?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Speed Run</h2>Keep track and improve the time of completion of each checkpoint and compare your best time with your current one.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Atmosphere</h2>Each zone has unique art, music, and special platforms that set the feel of the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Functionality</h2>The game is supported by a keyboard and controllers with haptic feedback.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Join our discord:</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>While descending you will face various challenges that you will overcome by rolling, jumping and avoiding taking fall damage.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/d19d55e8a5dec697111828dbdfe19bc1.poster.avif?t=1645525200\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/d19d55e8a5dec697111828dbdfe19bc1.webm?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/d19d55e8a5dec697111828dbdfe19bc1.mp4?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Note: You can expect 1-2 hours of gameplay.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>You are a peasant that decides to take up the challenge of pursuing the tyrant king's lost crown. Your competitiveness and determination will shape you and your family's future, and the future of Eggland.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/f25d488f74b0c032e29a84e7a52c166b.poster.avif?t=1645525200\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/f25d488f74b0c032e29a84e7a52c166b.webm?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/f25d488f74b0c032e29a84e7a52c166b.mp4?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Downhill</h2>Your journey begins at the castle and will continue through different lower landscapes.<br>While descending you may take fall damage that can crack or even break your egg.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/8eda22dee4d3a8253ddf6a85add0778e.poster.avif?t=1645525200\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/8eda22dee4d3a8253ddf6a85add0778e.webm?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790990/extras/8eda22dee4d3a8253ddf6a85add0778e.mp4?t=1645525200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Speed Run</h2>Keep track and improve the time of completion of each checkpoint and compare your best time with your current one.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Atmosphere</h2>Each zone has unique art, music, and special platforms that set the feel of the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Functionality</h2>The game is supported by a keyboard and controllers with haptic feedback.",
